title: The Clash HDtracks 24-96 [FLAC]
description:
The Clash is the eponymous debut studio album by English punk rock band the Clash. It was released on 8 April 1977, through CBS Records. This is the HDTracks High Res 24-bit 96kHz US release version.

So why listen to a punk album in high resolution audio? Well, give it a listen and judge for yourself. It's unfortunate that HDTracks decided to go with the US version, missing out on the original version of White Riot.

Omitted from the US version were the following tracks:

"Deny"
"Cheat"
"Protex Blue"
"48 Hours"
"White Riot" (original version)
